An act to add Chapter 4 (commencing with Section 11483) to Title 1 of Part 4 of the Penal Code, relating to crimes.

An act to add and repeal Section 17140.7 of the Revenue and Taxation Code, relating to taxation, to take effect immediately, tax levy.
An act to add Chapter 25 (commencing with Section 27050) to Division 20 of the Health and Safety Code, relating to reproductive health.
